{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"ImageTrackList.ready","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageTrackList/ready","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebCodecs_API\">WebCodecs API</a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Interfaces</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioData\"><code>AudioData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioDecoder\"><code>AudioDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioEncoder\"><code>AudioEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EncodedAudioChunk\"><code>EncodedAudioChunk</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EncodedVideoChunk\"><code>EncodedVideoChunk</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageDecoder\"><code>ImageDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageTrack\"><code>ImageTrack</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageTrackList\"><code>ImageTrackList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VideoDecoder\"><code>VideoDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VideoEncoder\"><code>VideoEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VideoColorSpace\"><code>VideoColorSpace</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VideoFrame\"><code>VideoFrame</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong><code>ready</code></strong> property of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageTrackList\"><code>ImageTrackList</code></a> interface returns a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> that resolves when the <code>ImageTrackList</code> is populated with <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageTrack\" title=\"tracks\"><code>tracks</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":false,"content":"<p>A <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> that resolves with <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/undefined\"><code>undefined</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The following example prints the value of <code>ready</code> to the console, this will be <code>undefined</code> once the promise resolves.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> tracks <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> imageDecoder<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tracks<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> ready <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> tracks<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ready<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ready<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/webcodecs/#dom-imagetracklist-ready","title":"WebCodecs"}],"query":"api.ImageTrackList.ready"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.ImageTrackList.ready","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageTrackList/ready/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Value","id":"value"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The ready property of the ImageTrackList interface returns a Promise that resolves when the ImageTrackList is populated with tracks.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-06-15T16:41:05.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/imagetracklist/ready","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/imagetracklist/ready/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/e1962f527cf027d307d4e2fd9ff06183da0cdb79","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageTrackList","title":"ImageTrackList"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageTrackList/ready","title":"ImageTrackList.ready"}],"pageTitle":"ImageTrackList.ready - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}